  "3333700": {
    "name": "国王的新牌",
    "steam_appid": 3333700,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尔等有幸体验朕这等伟大的国王的日常，是汝等之幸。挥舞“皇家令状”，操盘天下牌局！无论是召唤那些胆敢捣乱的鼠辈到王座厅接受审判，还是指挥卡牌军队横扫敌方疆土，尔等将感受到朕运筹帷幄的快感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/cb31bd426439d66f84146fb95c173890.avif?t=1772079823\" width=616 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尔等将统领一支由朕精心挑选的军队——包括“虚弱的火烈鸟”、“近视的鸡弓箭手”等奇葩角色，不要怜悯他们！在朕的旨意下，这些家伙会自动冲向前方，永不后退，朕留给他们的只有前进！若它们未胜利到达敌方阵地便倒下，便会永久殒命，牌组中再无踪影——这只是战争的一点必要的小代价！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/bece0381003b273593a4a9fc79bdbf27.poster.avif?t=1772079823\" width=1600 height=900 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/bece0381003b273593a4a9fc79bdbf27.webm?t=1772079823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/bece0381003b273593a4a9fc79bdbf27.mp4?t=1772079823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/7f7ea12419fd3c139ba29f4a22e1c751.avif?t=1772079823\" width=616 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了描述这伟大史诗，朕要求画师用充满中世纪风情的风格来如实记录。尔等将置身于王权与战争的恢弘舞台，切身实际体验朕那无比壮观的统治生涯！你看朕的画师画的多么惟妙惟肖，受伤后的卡牌一瘸一拐的身影，以及知道它们自己大难临头时的瑟瑟发抖，都体现的“栩栩如生”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/4eeda85892eccf79b5308261f80894bd.poster.avif?t=1772079823\" width=1600 height=900 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/4eeda85892eccf79b5308261f80894bd.webm?t=1772079823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/4eeda85892eccf79b5308261f80894bd.mp4?t=1772079823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/e341f3b71102e2d20b804f29bd6e0edb.avif?t=1772079823\" width=616 height=112 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >朕的军队种类多样（卡牌种类多样），从滑稽动物到英勇战士，尔等可随意搭配，他们大都也有着自己独特的技能和属性，利用好这些，打造属于朕的梦幻军团！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时候一些牺牲是必要的，那不过是朕成就伟业的垫脚石罢了！真正要考虑的是如何更好的搭配阵容，以达到更好的效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/f51885ae48b046d5a972a4dcc2709b03.poster.avif?t=1772079823\" width=1600 height=900 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/f51885ae48b046d5a972a4dcc2709b03.webm?t=1772079823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333700/extras/f51885ae48b046d5a972a4dcc2709b03.mp4?t=1772079823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
